The updates(Feb. 7) on the novel Coronavirus(2019-nCoV) 
in Republic of Korea
 
 
○ As of 7 February, 2020, there has been 1130 Patient Under Investigation(PUIs) with 24 confirmed cases, 842 cases already released after tested negative, and 264 cases currently being tested. The contacts of the confirmed cases are 1,368 in total, 9 of which were confirmed. 





